<h1>Recipe: <%=@recipe.name%></h1>
<h2>Ingredients: <%=@recipe.ingredients%></h2>
<h3>Cook Time: <%=@recipe.cook_time%> minutes</h3>

<p><a href="/recipes/<%=@recipe.id%>/edit">Edit this recipe</a> || <a href="/recipes/<%=@recipe.id%>/delete">Delete this recipe</a></p>

<p>
  The following button is redundant, I realize, but the specs for this assignment require it:
</p>
<form class="" action="/recipes/<%=@recipe.id%>/delete" method="post">
  <input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <input type="submit" name="submit" value="delete">
</form>
